data.text: Pako Jehova Nyasaye en gima ber kendo wero wende mapako nyingi
Nimar timbeni miya mor, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
Mano kaka tijeni dongo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
ni kata obedo ni joma timbegi richo nyalo loth kaka lum
To in, yaye Jehova Nyasaye, ibiro siko kimiyi duongʼ nyaka chiengʼ.
Nimar ka kuom adier, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
Isemiyo tungena odoko ma roboche ka tunge jowi;
Aseneno gi wengena ka iloyo wasika
Joma kare biro loth maber ka yiend othith,
Nikech opidhgi e od Jehova Nyasaye,
Kata hikgi oniangʼ to pod gininyag mana olemo,
ka gilando niya “Jehova Nyasaye oriere tir;
